Wizard: Force Shock, Garrisons Mighty Mana Shock (2.8 both) <br>
Difference: .45<br>
<br>
Level 24<br>
Mage: Shock of Spikes (3.5)<br>
Wizard: Frost Shock (3.15)<br>
Difference: .35<br>
